c: 47
v: 4
t: "Nimuramuka muhuye na babandi bahakanye (ku rugamba rugamije guhesha Allah icyubahiro), mujye mubakubita ku bikanu. Nimubanesha, mujye mubagira imbohe kugeza intambara irangiye. Hanyuma intambara nirangira, muzabarekure (ntacyo batanze) cyangwa batange inshungu. N’iyo Allah aza kubishaka, yari kubatsinda (nta ruhare mubigizemo); ariko (ibyo yabikoze) kugira ngo agerageze bamwe muri mwe akoresheje abandi. Naho babandi bishwe mu nzira ya Allah, ntazigera aburizamo ibikorwa byabo"